# Cursor Rules for Robotech Store Project

## Project Startup
When you open this project in Cursor, you can start the entire Robotech Store application by:

1. Opening the integrated terminal (Ctrl/Cmd + `)
2. Running: `./quick_start.sh`

Or simply double-click the `RobotechStore.app` file in the project folder (macOS).

## Available Commands
- `./quick_start.sh` - Start the entire project automatically
- `./start_project.sh` - Detailed startup with status messages
- `./test_startup.sh` - Verify all components are working

## URLs After Startup
- Home: http://localhost:8888/
- Products: http://localhost:8888/products
- Cart: http://localhost:8888/cart
- Orders: http://localhost:8888/orders

## Features Working
✅ Cart functionality
✅ User authentication (OTP login)
✅ Payment processing
✅ Order management
✅ MySQL database
✅ Responsive design
✅ Product catalog

The project will continue running even after closing Cursor - just keep the terminal window open!
